snippet.title: Return to Nangrim - Gameplay Trailer (Prototyping Winter 2018)
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for the upcoming fantasy adventure title "Arafinn - Return to Nangrim". Coming to PC and consoles. Gameplay footage from prototyping phase 2018.
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/860210/Return_to_Nangrim/
Connect with the devs: https://discord.gg/szEpMEvwCC
Stay tuned: https://return-to-nangrim.com

Soundtrack "The Mountain's Face" by Marco Valerio Antonini.
